#####
This is a MVC App


This app use Azure Key Vault to store the JWT Key

1. In production
Make sure deply VM has key vault set up already.

2. For dev env. 
dotnet user-secrets set "JwtOptions:Key" "xtelsndmeljrereirwelkrjewklrjewkl"

it will write the secret in local
%APPDATA%\Microsoft\UserSecrets\<GUID>\secrets.json.

you can check it by dotnet user-secrets list
Then you does not need to change any code in app. It will get key successsfully

#####
Other features
1. JWT Auth + Http.context User Claim
2. SignalR + JS for muti chating room service
1. Use serilog + JwtLoggingMiddlewware to rite user in Json file in rich text format
2. Use onlineUserTracker to track user numbers
3. Use global exception filter in app control/view setting 

